INSERT INTO sessions_stats (
                received_at,
                day,
                connection_time_ms,
                session_duration_min,
                two_hop,
                exit_id,
                error,
                country_code,
                from_mixnet) VALUES ($1::timestamptz, $2::date, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
